com.app.utility.validation

Class BootstrapValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.app.utility.validation.BootstrapValidator

  • public class BootstrapValidator
extends java.lang.Object
    BootstrapValidator validates each List of entries representing the CSV file. All methods invoked by BootstrapValidator affects the original data collection.
